data.title: ISSN Barcode (International Standard Serial Numbering Barcode)
data.meta_description: Description on the ISSN barcode (or International Standard Serial Numbering Barcode).
data.text: The ISSN is the standardized international code, which identifies any serial publication independently of its country of origin, its language or alphabet, or its frequency, medium, etc. ISSN barcode symbols begin with "977" followed by the first seven characters of the ISSN. The last character in the symbol is a check character, which is generated.
